data.description: Just like a model home with over $100k in upgrades since purchase! This one year old home is like new but BETTER! Low maintenance back yard in and complete with fire pit area. Upgraded paint and paneling throughout! Custom Paint colors, Upgraded luxury vinyl tile, and faux wood blinds throughout! Wonderful floorplan with everyday features which make life easier including downstairs bedroom and full bath, extra deep garage for home gym or workshop area, upstairs loft that could be converted to 5th bedroom, oversized and walk in closets, upstairs laundry room, large pantry, and mudroom with full closet in from garage. Home shows like a model! Must see!
